XTextDocument.ScriptText: sub Document_EventAfterPaintElement( sender as object , args as ElementPaintEventArgs) if TypeOf args.Element is XTextTableRowElement then dim txt as string = args.Element.GetAttribute("取消状态") if txt <> "" then ' 绘制取消状态文本 dim row as XTextTableRowElement = args.Element dim format as new StringFormat() format.Alignment = StringAlignment.Far format.LineAlignment = StringAlignment.Far dim font as new XFontValue("宋体" , 9 , FontStyle.Bold ) dim rect as RectangleF = args.ClientViewBounds rect.X += row.Cells(2).Left rect.Width = row.Cells(2).Width args.Graphics.DrawString(txt , font.Value, Brushes.Red, rect , format) format.Dispose() end if end if end sub
